title: The Fellows
author: nico0078
pages:
#- Fellowship

Fellowship was founded in late May by UnknownOreo1996, BluWolf_, Ryumast3r, and several others. Fellowship is a settlement in the (+,-) quadrant that was initially lead...
#- by UnknownOreo1996 that was based on the ideals of friendship, fellowship, and friendliness. Residents' houses varied in size and location from grand sky-scrapers and castles in the forest, to huts...
#- on the beach,  to log cabins on the top of some of the world's highest mountains.

Fellowship has many roads and accessways including stairs and ladders to reach the top of the mountains, canals..
#- and highways to travel long distances, and bridges, roads, and underwater passages to travel across the town and into other districts.

When founded, Fellowship was a part of the...
#- True Neutral League, and even though that organization has since disbanded, still considers its neighbors friends and trade partners.  

Fellowship has since gained popularity with...
#- the building of the Hexagon. As of January 20, 2014 the population of Fellowship was at 28 and Fellowship held third place in the Civcraft CIC. 
#- 